Chordate/Smokescreen:


Chordate and Smokescreen lead her to a room in the aft of the craft (near the 
back of the ship).  The door swishing open, Chordate motioned for her to go 
inside.  

"There you go.  Smokescreen here will come and get you when Kluster is ready."
